Conclusion

This project demonstrates how matrix factorization techniques like SVD and NMF can effectively build recommendation systems.
SVD provides better accuracy for dense latent patterns, while NMF offers better interpretability and handles sparse data efficiently.
Both methods help improve personalized movie recommendations.
